COVID-19 has only heightened existing issues in our mental health care system and we must make sure we are making longterm resources accessible and affordable for people who are dealing with depression, anxiety or PTSD during (and after) this crisis.  

https://t.co/rSvOUPeYy1

Don't let all of the talk about eventually reopening the economy fool you into thinking that it's safe to break social distancing procedures - it's not. We still have to stay inside unless absolutely necessary. This virus remains present and deadly in our communities.

In order to protect our communities during COVID-19, I believe that it's our job to encourage as many people as possible to #GetCovered. President Trump must put politics aside and do the right thing by opening a special enrollment period under the ACA immediately.

This just doesn't end, does it? President Trump is, once again, flying off the handle and politicizing a public address when the entirety of our country is looking for a leader. Every person in #PA01 deserves so much more than this sad display of incompetence.
